},{"pid":"60804c37e05c8e44fcf458fc643865bb4daf7dc0","tid":386854,"uid":1833,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:42:28.000Z","msg":"夜晚個餐前一個鐘食兩個火龍果<br />\n包你痾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922cd2862255564ca132428acb9b98fcba986640","tid":386854,"uid":30214,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"地門西梅汁"},{"pid":"57636e0b844744c8f779712c5051bba28f0065fa","tid":386854,"uid":72739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:44:27.000Z","msg":"乳酪呢？"},{"pid":"5da9f80624969ffde0528db1f6cc92d9aa7ce600","tid":386854,"uid":200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:45:20.000Z","msg":"綠豆"},{"pid":"58189adc5de7d72f11f62fcb62f57869e26be70e","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇中醫啦去..平時有無做運動?</blockquote><br />\n運動少，放工都攰到乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多唔多中醫煲埋藥，屋企知我睇實當我有絕症咁問到天荒地老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0382e9f84d1736348b32177116ba0acc391e33","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>綠豆</blockquote><br />\n苦瓜都開始食下，但係豆我真係頂唔順d口感，一食就嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9f1dbb892ae44f062a0591f8cae32e4d086656a","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:57:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地門西梅汁</blockquote><br />\n長期飲?"},{"pid":"70bf7bd6f1adf1ef0c1448d62b58b3ba07fc8c1e","tid":386854,"uid":27946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:03:06.000Z","msg":"凍奶茶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605502ef088d74f60ad3b3d6b3dda668b2fe92c8","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>地門西梅汁</blockquote><br />\n長期飲?</blockquote><br />\n我google見好春大支，其實有冇細支裝???"},{"pid":"c13ad3965d90db71980d9518ea9a9d5877dba755","tid":386854,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:37:26.000Z","msg":"你個食療法run左幾耐啊？以我經驗，要兩三星期起先開始正常返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗急<br />\n<br />\n利申，試過最差差唔多一/兩星期無法自然排出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 持續左半個月多d，食療法見效後日日相近時間就順暢排出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 形態理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我果時除左食水果菜飲果汁仲會狂飲奶，覺得奶最刺激腸胃，飲得夠多既會直頭整到肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無得唔出貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果次係自從一日肚痛後，就日日正常返<br />\n<br />\n唔想肚痛想健康d既就日日食下全麥包，最好每日一杯五青汁（上網睇材料），講緊自己用機榨，完全唔隔渣，最重要要食既係d渣，纖維係曬果度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家如果一兩日無貨或者得粒粒硬既就飲杯五青汁，之後就會有返完美作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b16a06dd6e19972842940a000de9130197aea9","tid":386854,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:38:53.000Z","msg":"西蘭花都非常唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69698e9ae508ccfaa3f555adf95dd8cf6a2872d1","tid":386854,"uid":57659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:42:54.000Z","msg":"去睇中醫 我諗係脾胃問題<br />\n我前幾日先去睇完 食左3日藥好番啲 唔好飲凍野 <br />\n之前都成日3,4日先有得去一次 如果唔係熱氣一般都係脾胃冇力"},{"pid":"7f87c412053256e16534eb1f81e9d003b0b4cd5d","tid":386854,"uid":137977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:44:21.000Z","msg":"多做運動 如果情況持續快啲睇醫生 驚你中屎毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed77f140aeb1ba293f236a6ac429ddfd23541842","tid":386854,"uid":139262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:44:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇中醫啦去..平時有無做運動?</blockquote><br />\n運動少，放工都攰到乜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多唔多中醫煲埋藥，屋企知我睇實當我有絕症咁問到天荒地老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家好多都係藥材粉沖熱水飲..好方便..運動都要做下得閒..幫助條腸"},{"pid":"c5fc5583d20129ba81d7db1256fffb604662a946","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多做運動 如果情況持續快啲睇醫生<span style=\"color: red;\"> 驚你中屎毒</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我通常都係三四日姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我見有人講成兩星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 究竟食幾十餐飯去哂邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb7d186e2cd9a382368472afe3a1fdb427fd665","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T10:18:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個食療法run左幾耐啊？以我經驗，要兩三星期起先開始正常返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗急<br />\n<br />\n利申，試過最差差唔多一/兩星期無法自然排出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 持續左半個月多d，食療法見效後日日相近時間就順暢排出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 形態理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我果時除左食水果菜飲果汁仲會狂飲奶，覺得奶最刺激腸胃，飲得夠多既會直頭整到肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無得唔出貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果次係自從一日肚痛後，就日日正常返<br />\n<br />\n唔想肚痛想健康d既就日日食下全麥包，最好每日一杯五青汁（上網睇材料），講緊自己用機榨，完全唔隔渣，最重要要食既係d渣，纖維係曬果度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家如果一兩日無貨或者得粒粒硬既就飲杯五青汁，之後就會有返完美作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾十餐飯去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n奶我一星期兩三盒啦，都係ok seven早餐個d"},{"pid":"c6b1c562ed506e1dc10760605ce426428c70e296","tid":386854,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>地門西梅汁</blockquote><br />\n長期飲?</blockquote><br />\n我google見好春大支，其實有冇細支裝???</blockquote><br />\n無 基本上係天然瀉藥嚟<br />\n飲一杯等一粒鐘睇下點 唔得就飲多杯<br />\n記得飲完唔好出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3478cd2d82fa0a4466a8c575dd742ebd49659c69","tid":386854,"uid":1593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T10:20:48.000Z","msg":"人既體質問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係好食菜既表示差唔多日日有屎屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c54b776546070a358ff5a365e4a04f1f4638628","tid":386854,"uid":137977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T10:22:02.000Z","msg":"大腸癌可以係其中一個成因 建議快啲做大腸鏡 大腸癌係香港殺人王頭三位 小心身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956500c88d313b4f253d6241d922b840f1c878b5","tid":386854,"uid":26110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T10:24:26.000Z","msg":"賴屎"},{"pid":"7c59705a33aa8a520ebf137dc804847a9a84586f","tid":386854,"uid":6640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T10:30:46.000Z","msg":"去濕毒 包你即屙"},{"pid":"eb4042f3e0b258d1e8b786c14830947cbb64a428","tid":386854,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T10:35:01.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n<br />\n可以試下每日早上一杯燕麥<br />\n如果覺得難食可以加多d水一下倒哂落口飲哂佢<br />\n<br />\n利申 成世人冇食過菜 以前極端便秘 而家每日都有大開勁舒暢<br />\n不過記得一定要早上食先有效"},{"pid":"940c6cabc8a32a8692d3c322cd511896a4bdc33d","tid":386854,"uid":29742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T10:41:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>地門西梅汁</blockquote><br />\n長期飲?</blockquote><br />\n我google見好春大支，其實有冇細支裝???</blockquote><br />\n無 基本上係天然瀉藥嚟<br />\n飲一杯等一粒鐘睇下點 唔得就飲多杯<br />\n記得飲完唔好出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成枝飲曬佢，包你痾到後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我第一次試呢個方法，痾左6，7次,後期痾埋水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8717c17d4d4596b7ecc60e56d8106d8aac508bb1","tid":386854,"uid":102888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T10:46:53.000Z","msg":"飲杯咖啡囉"},{"pid":"0ce8d35e589761d8fb13259d983d7c959cb735a8","tid":386854,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T10:53:35.000Z","msg":"西梅汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔好飲太多<br />\n我驚痾死你"},{"pid":"8f551a4f32ebcae0895f891b620c987bcb8ee6a8","tid":386854,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T10:54:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西梅汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔好飲太多<br />\n我驚痾死你</blockquote><br />\n另外朝頭早可以試下食麥皮<br />\n不過唔好用牛奶沖<br />\n用維他奶沖 麥精效果尤好"},{"pid":"516c3497349e2d8349b63294c5ef32a673d6f536","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T10:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西梅汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔好飲太多<br />\n我驚痾死你</blockquote><br />\n我見得大支裝"},{"pid":"1bc1c30cf10e8e9e21901649506bfa271fff4f8a","tid":386854,"uid":45352,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:01:10.000Z","msg":"屙唔出屎的第1天&nbsp;<br />\n感覺不太好...不過無理...&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n屙唔出屎的第2天&nbsp;<br />\n和女友談到2日無柯屎...她叫我食多d蕉..&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n屙唔出屎的第3天&nbsp;<br />\n周身唔舒服...不停食生果飲凍水了...都無用..把口有陣臭味&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n屙唔出屎的第4天&nbsp;<br />\n曾嘗試去廁所谷屎..不過無作用..面部谷了一兩粒暗倉&nbsp;<br />\n同事笑說道 : ha..你把口好臭wor !~&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n屙唔出屎的第5天&nbsp;<br />\n同女友做愛..濕吻時,女友說我口氣難頂,拒絕同我kiss..只幫我手淫草草了事...&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n屙唔出屎的第6天&nbsp;<br />\n買了甘油條...用後都係無作用...只bid到小小屎碎同屎汁出來...&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n屙唔出屎的第7天&nbsp;<br />\n面部嘴唇對上位置,生了數粒暗倉...早上剃鬚時更不小心割爆左一粒暗倉...血流滿嘴角...同事也開始埋怨我口臭的問題了...&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n屙唔出屎的第8天&nbsp;<br />\n女友拒絕了我的性要求..她和我出街..對我說 你個身同口氣好臭..塊面好多粒粒同暗倉..好難頂...叫我盡快去看醫生吧! 那天約會,我買了iphone4給她後..她便一聲不出走了...&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n屙唔出屎的第9天&nbsp;<br />\n口臭體臭問題很嚴重了..同事同我講野都故意離1-2米..有些同事更戴上口罩對我講野..狀什厭惡我...買了很多甘油條,浣腸器...都無作用..&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n屙唔出屎的第10天&nbsp;<br />\n女友多了很多籍口拒絕同我出街..後來她sms對我道..你而家身體成陣屎味谷出來..好難頂..塊面又多濃倉...我真係接受唔到lor ...我諗我地要冷靜下..&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n屙唔出屎的第11天&nbsp;<br />\n公司同事聯名寫email給老細投訴我身體發出烈臭.....影響工作士氣..卻send錯了給我看到...那天下班我決定去看醫生..食了藥都只係柯左小小屎碎&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n屙唔出屎的第12天&nbsp;<br />\nemail..sms 打電話都找不到女友了...晚上我在她公司樓下等她..等了半小時，有警察過來查問我，說有人報警受到跟蹤及騷擾.... 我知是她報警的..當時我眼淚不停流出來了.....&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n屙唔出屎的第13天&nbsp;<br />\n老細email同我講..公司生意不太好要栽員...願即時補兩個月人工 不過要我即刻走.....當天下班看見招職公司登請人的廣告...我看了眼淚不停流出來了..&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n屙唔出屎的第14天&nbsp;<br />\n身體發出強烈屎臭...面上長滿暗瘡..膚色己呈啡黃色..從FB看見女友info寫住..和XXX穩定交往.還用iphone4和那仆街自拍...她原來和另一個男仔一齊了...我眼淚不停流出來了...&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n屙唔出屎的第15天&nbsp;<br />\n屙得出屎了! 屙得出屎了!!!!!還屙了很多...我開心得流下眼淚!!不停流出來....可惜一齊都太遲了...."},{"pid":"4dab77c2f10d0f2119ab13c365a7451ac6de0222","tid":386854,"uid":30214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:21:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>西梅汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔好飲太多<br />\n我驚痾死你</blockquote><br />\n我見得大支裝</blockquote><br />\n直接買啦<br />\n你飲完之後果24個鐘可以唔洗出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f20ea25ce870fec366461675db2ec126da3c0d5","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>西梅汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔好飲太多<br />\n我驚痾死你</blockquote><br />\n我見得大支裝</blockquote><br />\n直接買啦<br />\n你飲完之後果24個鐘可以唔洗出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係為通一次wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通個個星期玩一次?定可以每幾日飲一杯"},{"pid":"26149cd9241986953bb910ff96ba28c6caf2373e","tid":386854,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:39:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n兩星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾十餐飯去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n奶我一星期兩三盒啦，都係ok seven早餐個d</blockquote><br />\n勁恐怖，果時仲要去緊長旅行餐餐食好飽但好耐先得果少少貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到去玩都去得唔爽，搞掂左就好開心，正常返後一次過排出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb6317b288a6ede4fcdf947f0c15fbae948067a","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg&h=1c11c863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n473ml都成25蚊，試下咩效果，ok就一星期飲支睇下點"},{"pid":"add08b3df74529521b3bea445a549d7d9248ece7","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:41:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg&h=1c11c863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n473ml都成25蚊，試下咩效果，ok就一星期飲支睇下點</blockquote><br />\n定分兩次飲好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd6d1cba9a83c49414fc9ec48352f561039cf45","tid":386854,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:42:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>西梅汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔好飲太多<br />\n我驚痾死你</blockquote><br />\n我見得大支裝</blockquote><br />\n直接買啦<br />\n你飲完之後果24個鐘可以唔洗出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係為通一次wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通個個星期玩一次?定可以每幾日飲一杯</blockquote><br />\n你呢d便秘惡性循環黎，硬果d乾到唔出黎，後面本身正常排緊隊果d係度被腸狂吸水到門口又變乾屎，之後又出唔到黎阻住後面，試下通一次先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e410bef44c053f45163ddfbdd939d92b92e11476","tid":386854,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:43:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg&h=1c11c863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n473ml都成25蚊，試下咩效果，ok就一星期飲支睇下點</blockquote><br />\n定分兩次飲好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我fd果時買佢話原來濃縮飲品黎，溝水開黎飲，唔知你呢支係咪啦"},{"pid":"ced9df6c03947a43e932e99b85207bd83824568a","tid":386854,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:46:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg&h=1c11c863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n473ml都成25蚊，試下咩效果，ok就一星期飲支睇下點</blockquote><br />\n邊度搵到細支?仲以為得大支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9243c3950698b682f51e93d3b0edee083d8d2ba9","tid":386854,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"我柯血已經柯到習以為常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無計 放工懶唔做運動"},{"pid":"63f31a0f99ac922768f6e692dea23a18b25fff29","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:48:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg&h=1c11c863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n473ml都成25蚊，試下咩效果，ok就一星期飲支睇下點</blockquote><br />\n定分兩次飲好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我fd果時買佢話原來濃縮飲品黎，溝水開黎飲，唔知你呢支係咪啦</blockquote><br />\n濃縮仲咁大支玩人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2392b266e29306b66286d70dbaaf2d779e58833c","tid":386854,"uid":92123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/195135_11ad0c558f13b3e4fd0a06a83cce20b9.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F195135_11ad0c558f13b3e4fd0a06a83cce20b9.jpeg&h=89871d10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食一粒加飲兩大杯水 試下得唔得<br />\n唔得去睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"49bc3c592f30e23bbec011993f60185612141407","tid":386854,"uid":138834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:52:39.000Z","msg":"要爽手,甘油泵<br />\n又爽又快,小心試完返唔到轉頭<br />\n<br />\n唔想插野入屎眼開發新性癖<br />\n就食D高油份堅果,例如腰果<br />\n食3碗以上<br />\n<br />\n都唔夠,就買支西梅汁,一野爆哂成支佢<br />\n<br />\n仲係唔得,檸檬汁撞奶,1L奶對1個檸檬,爆左佢"},{"pid":"231b2d79cee8466414a2d8ee3567063b9fa9ee7c","tid":386854,"uid":2514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f469c4fe67423672a71ac2fdf3995738ecba4d","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg&h=1c11c863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n473ml都成25蚊，試下咩效果，ok就一星期飲支睇下點</blockquote><br />\n邊度搵到細支?仲以為得大支<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大支的上面，16安士$24.9<br />\n<br />\n 32安士$50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw已飲，希望痾屎覆"},{"pid":"33c7e43f2d58f37268b0dd3688a0d007a5b72ce6","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:55:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我柯血已經柯到習以為常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無計 放工懶唔做運動</blockquote><br />\n就係怕遲早痾到外痔，出血加痛就仆街，我三十歲未夠呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487ff6118aeed8a8802bfaf37240c09133aa4486","tid":386854,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:59:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我柯血已經柯到習以為常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無計 放工懶唔做運動</blockquote><br />\n就係怕遲早痾到外痔，出血加痛就仆街，我三十歲未夠呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你我都係廿頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8200954275fad3e56d59c609629b912b0d6157ac","tid":386854,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:00:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我柯血已經柯到習以為常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無計 放工懶唔做運動</blockquote><br />\n就係怕遲早痾到外痔，出血加痛就仆街，我三十歲未夠呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你我都係廿頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本你開左個頭 就好易返發<br />\n就算你狂食菜又好 食個飯後果都好<br />\n你一早起身返工坐到收工 如果唔選擇做運動<br />\n好易又柯返血"},{"pid":"de39151dfa008cd743227cd1e94e69471dea9b83","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我柯血已經柯到習以為常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無計 放工懶唔做運動</blockquote><br />\n就係怕遲早痾到外痔，出血加痛就仆街，我三十歲未夠呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你我都係廿頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我28, 第一次出血4月........."},{"pid":"1de1d3ad1e0e443be3c001c97f44397b9bc200b0","tid":386854,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg&h=1c11c863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n473ml都成25蚊，試下咩效果，ok就一星期飲支睇下點</blockquote><br />\n定分兩次飲好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我fd果時買佢話原來濃縮飲品黎，溝水開黎飲，唔知你呢支係咪啦</blockquote><br />\n濃縮仲咁大支玩人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果知道血係因為粒痔瘡唔係內出血既，有乜好怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再睇醫生拎藥膏果d咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"607d9d3108c7a80ddbdb7b9566c7ce59a0560486","tid":386854,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:07:15.000Z","msg":"而家10個有8個都有，只係無講姐，you are not alone<br />\n<br />\n識fd有外痔 但無血無痛無癢"},{"pid":"e02579e8c7fcaf82edc3b854c9a7cf41597035f1","tid":386854,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:07:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我柯血已經柯到習以為常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無計 放工懶唔做運動</blockquote><br />\n就係怕遲早痾到外痔，出血加痛就仆街，我三十歲未夠呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你我都係廿頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我28, 第一次出血4月.........</blockquote><br />\n我二月開始出血 斷斷續續 有時日日都有血 有時好返一個星期又有返 柯屎痛出血試過 唔痛又試過 滴血試過 咩都試過 我日日有屎柯都係咁 唔關便唔便秘事<br />\n改善生活習慣應該會更好<br />\n利申我睇醫生指探過 無腹痛 體重無輕過 照常日日大食 都幾肯定係痔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a996c0c7db20eaee325c4f8bbb24d30372e70e86","tid":386854,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:09:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我柯血已經柯到習以為常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無計 放工懶唔做運動</blockquote><br />\n就係怕遲早痾到外痔，出血加痛就仆街，我三十歲未夠呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你我都係廿頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我28, 第一次出血4月.........</blockquote><br />\n我二月開始出血 斷斷續續 有時日日都有血 有時好返一個星期又有返 柯屎痛出血試過 唔痛又試過 滴血試過 咩都試過 我日日有屎柯都係咁 唔關便唔便秘事<br />\n改善生活習慣應該會更好<br />\n利申我睇醫生指探過 無腹痛 體重無輕過 照常日日大食 都幾肯定係痔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無塞過藥紓緩下，咁密都幾誇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6c4acd540a291a6909a957f78812cbc4571afcc","tid":386854,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:12:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我柯血已經柯到習以為常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無計 放工懶唔做運動</blockquote><br />\n就係怕遲早痾到外痔，出血加痛就仆街，我三十歲未夠呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你我都係廿頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我28, 第一次出血4月.........</blockquote><br />\n我二月開始出血 斷斷續續 有時日日都有血 有時好返一個星期又有返 柯屎痛出血試過 唔痛又試過 滴血試過 咩都試過 我日日有屎柯都係咁 唔關便唔便秘事<br />\n改善生活習慣應該會更好<br />\n利申我睇醫生指探過 無腹痛 體重無輕過 照常日日大食 都幾肯定係痔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無塞過藥紓緩下，咁密都幾誇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n塞過兩日 血量係少左 之後都無再塞了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次睇醫生都會順便問醫生拎盒藥<br />\n但係都無用過黎塞屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d8b53bf663bd7e3fe4b02212abb5b654f7a8ae","tid":386854,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:14:36.000Z","msg":"食穀類早餐<br />\n越似兔仔糧果D越有效"},{"pid":"0edc47b70b479602380b62b948f1b3be8e84a7f4","tid":386854,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:17:36.000Z","msg":"我fd塞藥係跟醫生講塞足一星期<br />\n之後打後幾個月都無血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1051fce15ca9228a2c6b3a86fe561512a43b2c17","tid":386854,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我fd塞藥係跟醫生講塞足一星期<br />\n之後打後幾個月都無血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生活習慣無改變過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n如果係既話 咁我都要開始塞了"},{"pid":"61736d1e76386ced85191968889d89a1c1466890","tid":386854,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:33:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我fd塞藥係跟醫生講塞足一星期<br />\n之後打後幾個月都無血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生活習慣無改變過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n如果係既話 咁我都要開始塞了</blockquote><br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢本身都唔係特別唔利便既生活習慣都唔知點解會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都會返發但都講緊好似係半年後既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d5de84063c2623a8a54e7279319dfe6d21b182","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T12:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F193931_e0517be40c5276a41005b1e3397f257a.jpg&h=1c11c863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n473ml都成25蚊，試下咩效果，ok就一星期飲支睇下點</blockquote><br />\n定分兩次飲好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我fd果時買佢話原來濃縮飲品黎，溝水開黎飲，唔知你呢支係咪啦</blockquote><br />\n濃縮仲咁大支玩人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果知道血係因為粒痔瘡唔係內出血既，有乜好怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再睇醫生拎藥膏果d咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n4月第一次出血睇,佢話9成係內痔,有睇我菊花,佢話除非連續出血一星期以上,否則係CANCER機會好低"},{"pid":"5eea963a1c073e6bf7941b0fd99970e0dda0c61f","tid":386854,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:19:22.000Z","msg":"最撚煩係少少急，如果夾硬谷可能出到，但夾硬谷就令痔瘡惡化，唔谷便秘又會痔瘡惡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw,支purple juice只係令我由唔急變少急，而家坐左五分鍾又唔想夾硬谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd12553182093af054922535ceb4cd2fee5718cd","tid":386854,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:50:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最撚煩係少少急，如果夾硬谷可能出到，但夾硬谷就令痔瘡惡化，唔谷便秘又會痔瘡惡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw,支purple juice只係令我由唔急變少急，而家坐左五分鍾又唔想夾硬谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成支隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da99ea0e966bbce6375f007a6cd2afb264e4f8e4","tid":386854,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"